article_title: Rand Paul: Americans Are Done With Trump, Support For Emminent Domain Will End Him
article_text:
SEN. RAND PAUL: I think people are ready to talk about issues.



BILL HEMMER, FNC: Where did this thing start with you and Trump?



RAND PAUL: Ha! Well, I think when you strike close to the mark you can really get somebody going. And the fact that I've been calling him a fake conservative, pointing out he supports Obamacare, supported the stimulus plan, and the one that rangles conservatives the most -- he supports taking private property through emminent domain through small property owners and giving it to big corporations. I don't know one conservative in America who supports that...



People are going to say, "my goodness, it is time to move on." And that time is now.
